{"tid":833894,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"下年過埋中秋就同女友結婚","createTime":"2018-09-24T00:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T20:32:19.000Z","uid":192189,"like":8,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"0a93930bf221883ec98f24829dff209b1f5953d0","tid":833894,"uid":192189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:09:18.000Z","msg":"行年28歲<br />\n搵緊月入中位數  戶口草左十萬準備下年過埋中秋同女友結婚<br />\n因為想要私人空間  所以會搬出去住<br />\n打算租間細細地村屋  $4000倒<br />\n再下年諗住有小朋友，所以佢應該都唔會做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個月慳慳地應該夠洗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最緊要一齊<br />\n有無同路人分享下？"},{"pid":"2cccf1a345fce1cb494f5caaf6de6b87e236d9e9","tid":833894,"uid":75359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:10:53.000Z","msg":"真心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06536cc3f6cb4f5c6457eebd4ed545090124a5a","tid":833894,"uid":123175,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:10:54.000Z","msg":"容我提早講句恭喜<br />\n另加加油"},{"pid":"690558615ae76bb1c5b7e8997b7a2537bc256c56","tid":833894,"uid":12618,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:10:56.000Z","msg":"四千蚊租屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n組合屋就有啲機既"},{"pid":"16eb07ce06f2ecfdc2a9cbeef72c6dfab29bd51d","tid":833894,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:12:54.000Z","msg":"不過你諗住邊到搵4000蚊租村屋？"},{"pid":"c38a9d8726166bd02f591c8bea99d0528659e90e","tid":833894,"uid":6907,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:21:12.000Z","msg":"唔好生仔啦"},{"pid":"9df797712bee774b2d880b767a2f0129377b06f8","tid":833894,"uid":192327,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:25:00.000Z","msg":"4000蚊租村屋邊到有？租到要用幾多時間返工？ 要搭幾錢車？<br />\n月入中位數姐係幾多呀？20k 真係唔夠養頭家。除非你2公婆都係唔洗比自己屋企<br />\n生細路 其實好事 方便申請公屋 但生細路頭一兩年條數好大<br />\n無返150k 比個細路同老婆燒下 <br />\n<br />\n仲有儲錢去買樓呢?當你唔買樓 都要儲返少少旁下身掛<br />\n<br />\n結婚細搞 晝龜就算 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左加油 共勉之 我都唔敢講太多放棄的地方"},{"pid":"07ad0b3b030a67366d19ecac12e23e656ab069c9","tid":833894,"uid":195858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:26:06.000Z","msg":"恭喜巴打<br />\n同年嘅我睇得好開心"},{"pid":"db50915d28a8a269f0ddc1c78be47decd3cc9c54","tid":833894,"uid":85219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:27:08.000Z","msg":"得你一個份糧養得起個細路咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ddc5aa6d037d66843365b4fcf96fa38578c3565","tid":833894,"uid":207009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:29:12.000Z","msg":"有夢想係好事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"040553c9324f837b94c5edcbc4734de3fe6e6db6","tid":833894,"uid":194882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:29:23.000Z","msg":"恭喜巴打<br />\n祝你有個美滿人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba0632cb9a0af3e4dede659e41af9592b64831f","tid":833894,"uid":56401,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:43:06.000Z","msg":"窮撚都學人生 笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過多十幾年又到佢個仔上連登屌佢個廢中老豆"},{"pid":"42483ee1ca0cb37c754382910bb65dc8a3dba29d","tid":833894,"uid":56618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:44:53.000Z","msg":"時光機？"},{"pid":"0eedb6a673d766093b2473b07c6a317adfe7b60a","tid":833894,"uid":33872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中位數係咪即係20k唔夠？"},{"pid":"6f3c17f5c229a4f31f24ba2591e94b9079685dca","tid":833894,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:48:49.000Z","msg":"恭喜<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"2f48a267338648a0c64e18258e6fd5b1f8439bbf","tid":833894,"uid":10844,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T01:01:00.000Z","msg":"如果係連登中位數都應該ok"},{"pid":"8d9ce50dd287970be6899ae2b261a54d2715f728","tid":833894,"uid":74259,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T01:07:05.000Z","msg":"小弟同女友行年21 <br />\n兩個都係搵緊19k 20k 咁<br />\n都係想結婚 <br />\n但真係計唔掂數 <br />\n租樓兩個人住冇錢淨<br />\n我計鬆d當加埋有40k <br />\n租個單位仔～270呎 起碼要11k <br />\n40-11=29<br />\n一個人日常使費慳慳地點都要6k<br />\n29-12=17<br />\n再扣多1人1k 老強<br />\n17-2=15 <br />\n咁始終唔可以太苦悶 咁預一個月有3k 一齊去拍拖啦 <br />\n15-3=12<br />\n再扣埋條家用  水電煤 耐唔耐要買下ge日用品又病下 其實都冇咩得淨了 <br />\n而4k 村屋俾盡都係冇200呎 仲要貴電費 遠輕鐵 冇管理 隨時日日個幾兩個鐘一程車 甚至你女朋友夜返俾隻蝻姦左都搵唔番個犯"},{"pid":"41c89de41b79b530bf72332cfe695fa1b96a6e06","tid":833894,"uid":57513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T01:23:16.000Z","msg":"邊度4000蚊租屋?<br />\n交通好唔方便?"},{"pid":"bb0eb68d9ee864d723932579ab51c6de46591d5b","tid":833894,"uid":76105,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:13:21.000Z","msg":"巴打入去坐咗十年？？？<br />\n十萬就結婚同埋4000租屋？ <br />\n劏房租兩個床位都唔夠錢喎你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406b0ca326541e508d90bf148adce5aff06a81ba","tid":833894,"uid":159935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:18:08.000Z","msg":"4000蚊想有村屋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我屋企地下出面有個組合屋36呎，夠唔夠用？"},{"pid":"39786eb00eb5dff1e3f4136da959aa216c105ad1","tid":833894,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"